<D>__{kane's empire, in its glory, held dominion over thirty seven newpapers, thirteen magazines, a radio network. an empire upon an empire. the first of grocery stores, paper mills, apartment buildings, factories, forests, ocean liners an empire through which for fifty years flowed, in an unending stream, the wealth of the earth's third richest gold mine... famed in american legend is the origin of the kane fortune... how, to boarding housekeeper mary kane, by a defaulting boarder, in 1868 was left the supposedly worthless deed to an abandoned mine shaft: the colorado lode. the magnificent enquirer building of today.}
